    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"This character has poison running through his veins. His vision is blurred, his speech slurred and it takes a great deal of effort for him to move in a coordinated fashion. The effect will slowly wear off over [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.NegativeValue + \"]\" + this.m.TurnsLeft + \"[/color] more turn(s).\""
